> 
> 1) Start Imagine.
> 
> 2) Open a shell window.
> 
> 3) CHANGETASKPRI -1
> 
> 4) RUN WORK:IMAGINE/IMAGINE
> 
> 5) CHANGETASKPRI -2
> 
